# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# OurBlock Docker Build - Ignore Patterns
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Git
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes

# Development files
.envrc
.direnv
.vscode
*.md
!README.md

# Nix
flake.lock
result
result-*

# Rust build artifacts (we build fresh in container)
target/
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock

# Node modules (we install fresh in container)
node_modules/
ui/node_modules/
.pnpm-store/

# Test files
**/test/
**/tests/
**/*.test.ts
**/*.test.tsx
**/*.spec.ts
**/*.spec.tsx

# IDE and editor files
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# Environment files (secrets)
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
*.pem
*.key
.lair_passphrase

# Build outputs that shouldn't be in image
dist/
build/
*.dna
*.happ

# Documentation
docs/
*.md
!deploy/README.md

# CI/CD
.github/
.gitlab-ci.yml
.travis.yml
Jenkinsfile

# Docker files (don't copy Docker stuff into Docker)
docker-compose*.yaml
Dockerfile*
.docker/
